C-Sort Task for Week 5 iP

Chatbot Window: Does not support scrolling

Users are unable to view previous messages once they overflow
beyond visible window.

Replace VBox with a ScrollPane that wraps the VBox, allowing
users to scroll manually while still displaying new messages
properly.

ScrollPane provides built-in scrolling functionality, ensuring
that users can freely navigate past messages while maintaining
smooth auto-scrolling for new messages.

-----------------------------------------------

DialogBox - Messages with long content were getting cut off

Long messages were not fully displayed, making it difficult
to read the entire content.

Set text.setMaxWidth(Double.MAX_VALUE) in DialogBox to allow
messages to fully expand

Using Double.MAX_VALUE ensures that messages dynamically adjust
to available space rather than being forcibly constrained
